data.title: Free Images, Backgrounds and Photos • picjumbo
data.meta_description: Free images, free photos, backgrounds and wallpapers. Download the best images for your websites, templates, blogs or designs.️ It's free!
data.text:
What is free stock photo?

Free stock photo is a photo that can be downloaded free of charge and used in various ways, both in personal and often in commercial projects.

Free images from picjumbo have no watermark and all photos are free of charge. We have free images for commercial use, free photos, backgrounds, HD wallpapers, royalty-free images free of charge and more.

What is picjumbo?

picjumbo is a free image website created in 2013 by designer & photographer Viktor Hanacek. It all started when all of the regular stock photo sites rejected his photos for "lack of quality".

Two years later, people have downloaded more than two and half million free pictures from picjumbo! Now it’s one of the best free stock photo websites with thousands of very high-resolution free images.

What free images can I find on picjumbo?

There are a lot of categories ranging from business photos, animal pictures, abstract images to nature images or technology photos. Just use Search bar in header or Categories in menu.

Most popular & best free images are business photos, nature images, technology photos and finally backgrounds or free wallpapers.

Are all free images FREE?

Yes, here on picjumbo all of our published photos and images are free to download and can be used even in commercial projects (unless it’s against the law, obviously).

You don’t even have to credit the author, but it’s very appreciated. If you want, you can support the photographer directly via Donate/Buy me a coffee buttons.
